  },
  {
   "type": "title2",
   "html": "1864 － 1911"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ かわかみ・おとじろう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n俳優、落語家、新聞記者、<a href=\"../p/ksadayak.html\">川上貞奴</a>の夫"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"02k.html\">一覧　（カ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E5%25B7%259D%25E4%25B8%258A%2520%25E9%259F%25B3%25E4%25BA%258C%25E9%2583%258E\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　福岡県出身。14歳で上京、職を転々。郷里で政治運動に行い、投獄と釈放を繰り返す。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　政談演説が禁止されると、大阪の寄席に登場、時局風刺の漫談を演じる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　京都、東京と出演の場を求め、中村座公演で、幕間に演じたオッペケペー節が評判を呼ぶ。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　パリに赴き帰国、西洋演劇の意匠を取り入れた翻案劇「意外」の上演などで大成功。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　東京・神田に川上座を設立するも、代議士に立候補して落選し、人手に渡る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　妻の<a href=\"../p/ksadayak.html\">貞奴</a>とともに一座を率いて欧米に公演し、好評を得る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　晩年は興行師としての仕事に専心し大阪に帝国座を建てた。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
